item.title: Petzl Scirocco Vizir adaptor
item.description:
This is an adaptor to mount the Petzl Vizir visor to the Petzl Scirocco climbing helmet. This only works with the Vizir and Vizir Shadow from before 2019, as the new visors are only compatible with their professional hard-hat lineup.

Is designed to be printed with tpu filament (tested with ninjaflex), after printing, use a 20-25mm M4 flathead screw through the printed part and the holes in the helmet, and hook on the visor as you screw it in.

item.title: Customizer: Adaptateur de bride de vidange Somatherm (drain washing machine adapter)
item.description:
Cet adaptateur permet de brancher le kit de bride de vidange (Somatherm) à un tuyau d'évacuation plus gros (diamètre 50 par exemple).
Celui-ci est personnalisable selon le diamètre du tuyau à connecter.
En effet, il s'adapte seulement au tuyau PVC 32 ou 40 d'origine.

Le STL d'exemple permet de connecter un tuyau PVC en diamètre 50.

Attention: l'outil de perforation n'est pas compatible (double pas de vis), il faut donc perforer le tuyau avant l'installation (avec une perceuse par exemple).

This adapter allows to connect the drain adaptater to different size of pipes.
The original kit only works with PVC diameters 32 or 40.
The design can be customized to a different pipe size (>=40), in the STL it's for diameter 50.

Warning: the cutting tool is not compatible as it requires a double threading, a manual perforation of the PVC pipe is needed.

item.title: Thermomix TM6 (and TM5) Egg Splitter and Funnel
item.description:
2 objects to be printed here - a funnel and an egg splitter that both fit in the hole of the Thermomix cover.

I designed them for the TM6 but the hole size is the same so they should also work for TM5.

Use FOOD SAFE filament- PETG for example.

I printed with 3 walls which makes it sturdy.

Tip to use the egg splitter:

  • Put in the cap hole
  • Crack the egg in it
  • Slowly spin the egg splitted in the hole (not to hard)

I included the Fusion 360 file if anybody wants to modify it.

item.title: Pipe Clamp Adapter
item.description:
This is an adapter for firmly grasping the pipe without crushing it. Compatible with pipes from 2 mm to 12 mm.

[Design points]
-A pair of adapters are combined so it's easy to find from the toolbox
-Since the adapter can be opened with one hand like a clip, it is easy to pinch the pipe and set it in a vise.
-Since the size are 1 mm steps, it can handle an intermediate pipe size (for example, 9.5 mm).

-[print conditions]
-filament: PETG
-support: no
-brim: no
-raft: doesn't matter

item.title: Customizable Stand for Articulated Dragon
item.description:
My design inspired from https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:5178556

This is fully customizable, you can print off your own designs to attach to base and top of pole, or not.

Use glue to attach pole to stand.

I have included separate files to be able to print the base and pole in different colors, just glue together. I also included an alternate for top of pole.

Not a big fan of supports, All files printed support free.

I printed the rings in the same color as the stand Rings do have different dimensions you will need 2 of the Top/Middle ring.

Find the Dragon STL here: https://cults3d.com/en/3d-model/game/articulated-dragon-mcgybeer

item.title: Adaptateur ventilation noctua hot end pour ender 3 max
item.description:
adaptateur pour installer des ventilateurs noctua 40x40 sur le hot end de la ender 3 max, il on été prévu pour installer un crtouch. Sinon il suffit de reproduire la symétrie de celui qui na pas la fixation, Mettre des supports partout avec un angle de 75, motif du support ligne, bordure a 5 de largeur et ca s'imprime facilement. Je recommande le PETG il sera plus résistant que le PLA, Il faudra changer les vis de fixation plus longue.

https://www.amazon.fr/gp/product/B00O9Y6BFG/ref=ppx_yo_dt_b_asin_image_o06_s00?ie=UTF8&psc=1

celle-ci seront recouper a la bonne longueur.
